snippet.title: Don't Escape 2 - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
A sequel to Don't Escape - anti-escape-the-room Flash game from 2013.
Coming soon to Armor Games!
Music used in trailer (as well as in the game) - Metaphysik - by Kevin MacLeod - http://incompetech.com/wordpress/2014/12/metaphysik/
